data.description: Bright 3 bed 2 bath tri-level style home located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Marianna Farms in Loveland! Open main floor plan with vaulted ceilings & brand new luxury vinyl plank throughout kitchen & dining. 2 bedrooms + full bath upstairs, bedroom & 3/4 bath downstairs plus laundry & additional family room. No HOA or Metro District! Great outdoor space with patio, fenced yard & garden bed. Property needs some TLC & is Priced accordingly. All kitchen appliances stay, including brand new dishwasher!
